package.name: sfExtjsThemePlugin
package.summary: A theme plugin returning list and edit panels, with an extended generator capable of handling foreign-fields
package.description: This plugin returns edit and list panels, which are extensions of the Ext.Panel Object. The generator can handle foreign-fields, and allowes to define properties from the Ext-api with the params parameter in your generator.yml (for fields, list, edit and pages)
package.notes: This plugin is still in active development, but getting usable.
